column4: I need some help, whenever I plug in my headphones into my headphone jack the sound just comes through the computer speaks, not the headphones.
I need some help, whenever I plug in my headphones into my headphone jack the sound just comes through the computer speaks, not the headphones.
you checked the forums yet? I see a question like that - or about like that - in here every week/few days.. never seen a 'quick fix' however.
I'm in the main folder.. Not in SRC or anything.
and any errors its giving are?
It just says "The program 'qmake' can be found in the following packages.
so its telling you that qmake is NOT installed....
When I type in make after qmake I get an error
Something something fatal error: QApplication: No such file or directory
you proberly need to isntall extra dev packages..
read the error messages and qmake/make output and figure it out. or if the pacakge is allready in teh repos. you can use the 'apt-get build-deps pacakgename'
